F.2 CBF Safe Set Visualization

The safe set $\mathcal{C}$ is defined by the intersection of three constraints:

\mathcal{C} = \{ x : h_q(x) \ge 0 \} \cap \{ x : h_n(x) \ge 0 \} \cap \{ x : h_{q_{dyn}}(x) \ge 0 \} 

Where:

· $h_q(x) = q_{max} - q_{stag}(x)$ (Heat flux margin)
· $h_n(x) = n_{max} - n(x)$ (Load factor margin)
· $h_{q_{dyn}}(x) = q_{dyn,max} - \frac{1}{2}\rho v^2$ (Dynamic pressure margin)

